<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA31">
<l>puriyorukai paṟṟiyōr poṉṉāḻi yēnti</l>
<l>yariyuruvu māḷuruvu māki – yeriyuruva</l>
<l>vaṇṇattāṉ mārpiṭanta mālaṭiyai yallāṉmaṟ</l>
<l>ṟeṇṇattā ṉāmō vimai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Grasping in one hand the conch, holding in the other the golden discus,</l>
<l>being in lion form and in man form, Māl who dug up the chest</l>
<l>of him with flame[-like] beautiful colour, is it possible to regard</l>
<l>something other than his feet, [even] for a moment?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
